                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Live to twelve thousand viewers, walking the strip, narrating the collapse of a currency in real time. Great numbers. Terrible economy. The two are related and I try not to think about how."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Chat wants me to knock on the tower door. Chat can find a new streamer. That door does not open for the likes of me and I would like to keep my likeness."
                        }
                    ],
